2Ô∏è‚É£ Consistency and Quality: Robust internal processes promote consistency in delivering products and services, which leads to customer satisfaction and loyalty. By standardizing procedures and implementing quality control measures, organizations can ensure that every interaction and deliverable meets or exceeds customer expectations.

