5Ô∏è‚É£ Risk Management and Compliance: Internal processes play a pivotal role in mitigating risks and ensuring compliance with legal and regulatory requirements. By implementing checks and balances, organizations can identify and address potential risks proactively, safeguarding their reputation and minimizing financial and legal implications.

